---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="IV Sedation" 
  category="Comfort Dentistry"
  description="Deep sedation for nervous patients. Currently, IV Sedation is only available in our Garden City location."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1631217868264-e5b90bb7e133?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Comfort for Anxious Patients</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Deep sedation for nervous patients helps you receive necessary dental care in complete comfort. 
        Our IV sedation creates a deeply relaxed state where you'll have little to no memory of the procedure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Important Location Notice -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-200/50 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
            <strong>Currently, IV Sedation is only available in our Garden City location</strong> 
            (211-2305 McPhillips Street). Please contact this office directly to schedule your 
            sedation appointment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      What is IV Sedation?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Intravenous (IV) sedation, also known as "twilight sleep," is a form of conscious sedation 
        that helps patients achieve a deep state of relaxation during dental procedures. Unlike general 
        anesthesia, you remain conscious and can respond to verbal cues, but you'll feel extremely 
        relaxed and have little to no memory of the treatment.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-4 bg-accent-50 rounded-lg">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Deep Relaxation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Feel completely calm and at ease throughout treatment</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-4 bg-primary-50 rounded-lg">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Conscious Sedation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Remain conscious and able to respond while deeply relaxed</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Minimal Memory</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Little to no recollection of the dental procedure</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Who Benefits from IV Sedation?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Ideal Candidates</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>High dental anxiety or phobia:</strong> Patients who avoid dental care due to fear</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Complex or lengthy procedures:</strong> Multiple extractions, oral surgery, implants</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Gag reflex issues:</strong> Strong gag reflex that interferes with treatment</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Physical disabilities:</strong> Conditions that make positioning difficult</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Traumatic dental experiences:</strong> Previous negative dental encounters</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">Medical Considerations</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          While IV sedation is safe for most patients, certain medical conditions require special consideration:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Heart conditions or blood pressure issues</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Respiratory problems or sleep apnea</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Liver or kidney disease</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Drug allergies or medication interactions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-yellow-500 mt-1">•</span>
            <span>Pregnancy or nursing</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="bg-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-3 mt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800">
            <strong>Important:</strong> A thorough medical history review is required before sedation
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The IV Sedation Process
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Pre-Treatment -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Pre-Treatment Consultation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              We'll review your medical history, discuss your anxiety concerns, and explain the sedation process. 
              Pre-operative instructions include fasting for 6-8 hours before treatment.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Requirements:</strong> Adult escort required for transportation home after treatment
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Treatment Day -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Treatment Day Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              We'll take your vital signs, place monitoring equipment, and establish IV access. 
              Sedation medication is administered gradually until you reach optimal comfort level.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Monitoring:</strong> Heart rate, blood pressure, and oxygen levels continuously monitored
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- During Treatment -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">During Your Procedure</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              You'll remain conscious but deeply relaxed. Local anesthetic is still used for complete comfort. 
              The sedation level can be adjusted throughout the procedure as needed.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Experience:</strong> Time will seem to pass quickly with little memory of the procedure
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Recovery -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Post-Treatment Recovery</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Recovery time varies but typically takes 30-60 minutes. We monitor you until you're stable and alert 
              enough for discharge with your escort. Full recovery takes several hours.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Restrictions:</strong> No driving, operating machinery, or important decisions for 24 hours
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Safety & Monitoring
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Safety Protocols</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Board-certified anesthesia provider supervision</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>State-of-the-art monitoring equipment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Emergency medications and equipment on-site</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Comprehensive pre-sedation health screening</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Post-sedation recovery monitoring</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Continuous Monitoring</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Pulse Oximetry</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Blood oxygen levels monitored continuously</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">EKG Monitoring</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Heart rhythm and rate tracking</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Blood Pressure</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Regular blood pressure measurements</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-1">Capnography</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Carbon dioxide levels in exhaled breath</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Preparing for IV Sedation
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-700 mb-4">Before Your Appointment</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>No food or drink</strong> for 6-8 hours before treatment</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Arrange for a responsible adult escort</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Take only prescribed medications as directed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Wear comfortable, loose-fitting clothing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Remove contact lenses, jewelry, and nail polish</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 mb-4">After Your Appointment</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Rest at home for the remainder of the day</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Have your escort stay with you for several hours</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Start with clear fluids, advance to light foods</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Follow post-operative care instructions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Avoid alcohol and sedating medications</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Comfortable Dental Care for Anxious Patients
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Don't let dental anxiety prevent you from getting the care you need. Our IV sedation service 
        at our Garden City location provides a comfortable, stress-free dental experience.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-accent-200">
        <strong>Garden City Location:</strong> 211-2305 McPhillips Street
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
